Synopsis: Converts a file's use of PSFramework messages to strings.
Description: Converts a file's use of PSFramework messages to strings.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Convert-PSMDMessage -Path 'C:\Scripts\logrotate.ps1' -OutPath 'C:\output'
Converts all instances of writing messages in logrotate.ps1 to use strings instead.
